880
01:25:14,181 --> 01:25:16,081
Stillson! Stillson!

881
01:25:16,149 --> 01:25:18,414
Stillson! Stillson!

882
01:25:21,923 --> 01:25:23,857
Good to see you.

883
01:25:26,093 --> 01:25:27,958
Hi. How are you?

884
01:25:28,029 --> 01:25:29,861
Good to see you.

885
01:25:29,932 --> 01:25:31,957
Hi. How are you?

886
01:25:32,034 --> 01:25:36,266
How you doing?
Good to see you.

887
01:25:46,049 --> 01:25:47,812
Do it, General.

888
01:25:47,884 --> 01:25:49,818
You're insane.
I won't.

889
01:25:49,886 --> 01:25:54,790
Do it! You'll go down
in history with me!

890
01:25:54,859 --> 01:25:58,295
As what? The world's
greatest mass murderers?

891
01:25:58,362 --> 01:26:00,227
You cowardly bastard!

892
01:26:00,297 --> 01:26:03,164
You're not the voice
of the people!

893
01:26:03,234 --> 01:26:05,465
The people speak through me!

894
01:26:05,537 --> 01:26:10,133
It came to me while I slept--
my destiny.

895
01:26:10,208 --> 01:26:14,167
I must get up now
and fulfill my destiny!

896
01:26:14,246 --> 01:26:18,650
Put your hand on that,
or I'll hack it off!

897
01:26:18,718 --> 01:26:20,652
Do it!

898
01:26:32,933 --> 01:26:34,867
May God forgive me.

899
01:26:45,146 --> 01:26:47,137
Congratulations, General.

900
01:26:49,784 --> 01:26:52,720
Complete the sequence,
Mr. President.

901
01:27:11,441 --> 01:27:13,500
My destiny.

902
01:27:21,819 --> 01:27:23,753
Thank you, Sonny.

903
01:27:32,097 --> 01:27:34,930
Let them come up.

904
01:27:36,335 --> 01:27:39,772
Mr. President, we have
a diplomatic solution.

905
01:27:39,839 --> 01:27:42,273
Mr. Vice President,
Mr. Secretary,

906
01:27:42,342 --> 01:27:44,606
the missiles are flying.

907
01:27:44,677 --> 01:27:47,771
Hallelujah.
Hallelujah.

908
01:27:53,654 --> 01:27:56,020
You okay, Greg?

909
01:27:58,158 --> 01:28:00,922
Get out!

910
01:28:00,995 --> 01:28:02,930
Stillson! Stillson!

911
01:28:02,998 --> 01:28:05,831
Stillson! Stillson!

912
01:28:05,900 --> 01:28:08,391
Stillson! Stillson!

913
01:28:18,214 --> 01:28:22,548
If you could go back
in time to Germany,

914
01:28:22,618 --> 01:28:25,315
before Hitler came to power,

915
01:28:25,389 --> 01:28:27,823
knowing what you know now,

916
01:28:27,891 --> 01:28:30,382
would you kill him?

917
01:28:30,460 --> 01:28:34,021
Is that why
you sent for me,

918
01:28:34,097 --> 01:28:37,329
to ask me this, uh...
this question?

919
01:28:41,406 --> 01:28:44,842
I have to talk
to you, Sam,

920
01:28:44,909 --> 01:28:48,209
because I've had
another episode.

921
01:28:48,280 --> 01:28:50,214
Oh, yes?

922
01:28:50,282 --> 01:28:53,149
Go on.

923
01:28:53,218 --> 01:28:56,813
I've been tutoring
this boy named Stuart.

924
01:28:56,889 --> 01:29:00,155
In the vision,
I saw him drown.

925
01:29:00,226 --> 01:29:02,717
But that's
not the point.

926
01:29:02,796 --> 01:29:05,822
In the vision,
something was missing.

927
01:29:05,899 --> 01:29:08,697
How-- How do you mean?

928
01:29:08,768 --> 01:29:13,934
It was like... a blank spot,
a dead zone.

929
01:29:19,914 --> 01:29:22,508
First of all, tell me,

930
01:29:22,583 --> 01:29:25,678
did the boy in fact drown?

931
01:29:25,754 --> 01:29:28,450
His father wanted him
to play hockey.

932
01:29:28,523 --> 01:29:30,787
I talked him out of it.
The boy's alive.

933
01:29:30,859 --> 01:29:35,695
Ah. Yes.

934
01:29:35,765 --> 01:29:39,201
Don't you see
how clear it is?

935
01:29:39,268 --> 01:29:44,103
Not only can you
see the future, you can--

936
01:29:44,173 --> 01:29:47,610
- I can change it.
- You can change it, exactly.

937
01:29:49,179 --> 01:29:51,272
Here.

938
01:29:53,851 --> 01:29:57,446
Yes, John.
That is your-- your dead zone.

939
01:29:57,521 --> 01:29:59,547
The possibility of...

940
01:29:59,624 --> 01:30:03,458
of altering the outcome
of your premonitions...

941
01:30:03,528 --> 01:30:07,464
it's fascinating.
Let me make a note.

942
01:30:09,201 --> 01:30:12,227
What about my question?

943
01:30:12,304 --> 01:30:14,795
Huh?

944
01:30:14,874 --> 01:30:18,640
Oh, you mean
the one about Hitler?

945
01:30:18,711 --> 01:30:22,478
- What would you do?
- I don't like this.

946
01:30:22,549 --> 01:30:24,915
What are you getting at?

947
01:30:24,985 --> 01:30:28,477
What would you do?
Would you kill him?

948
01:30:31,725 --> 01:30:33,660
All right.

949
01:30:33,728 --> 01:30:37,164
All right.
I'll give you an answer.

950
01:30:37,231 --> 01:30:39,791
I'm a man of medicine.

951
01:30:39,867 --> 01:30:43,826
I'm expected to save lives
and ease suffering.

952
01:30:43,905 --> 01:30:45,840
I love people.

953
01:30:45,908 --> 01:30:48,342
Therefore,
I would have no choice

954
01:30:48,410 --> 01:30:52,346
but to kill
the son of a bitch.

955
01:30:58,755 --> 01:31:01,189
You'd never get away alive.

956
01:31:01,257 --> 01:31:04,693
It doesn't matter.
I would kill him.

957
01:31:04,761 --> 01:31:07,227
Nasdro via. Skol.

958
01:32:31,653 --> 01:32:33,587
"Dear Sarah,

959
01:32:33,655 --> 01:32:37,250
lt is a hard letter to write,

960
01:32:37,325 --> 01:32:39,691
so I'll make it short.

961
01:32:39,761 --> 01:32:43,095
I can't go on hiding anymore.

962
01:32:43,165 --> 01:32:45,599
That's what l've been doing--

963
01:32:45,668 --> 01:32:47,602
running and hiding.

964
01:32:47,670 --> 01:32:50,264
I had this
figured out all wrong.

965
01:32:50,339 --> 01:32:54,276
I always thought
my power was a curse,

966
01:32:54,344 --> 01:32:58,280
but now I can see it 's a gift.

967
01:32:58,348 --> 01:33:01,784
By the time you get this letter,

968
01:33:01,852 --> 01:33:03,786
it'll be all over.

969
01:33:03,855 --> 01:33:06,289
You never will understand why.

970
01:33:06,357 --> 01:33:10,794
Nobody ever will,
but I know what I'm doing.

971
01:33:10,862 --> 01:33:13,126
And I know I'm right.

972
01:33:13,197 --> 01:33:19,068
Just remember there's never
been anyone for me except you.

973
01:33:20,706 --> 01:33:25,143
Just wasn't in the cards
for us, I guess.

974
01:33:25,210 --> 01:33:27,441
I'll always love you,
Sarah.

975
