Johnny."

976
01:35:39,690 --> 01:35:41,817
How you doing?

977
01:35:52,070 --> 01:35:55,471
Thanks very much.
What's your name?

978
01:35:56,541 --> 01:35:58,476
Greg, my husband Walt.

979
01:35:58,544 --> 01:36:00,978
Hi, Walt.
This your baby?

980
01:36:02,215 --> 01:36:04,615
Bring him up on stage.

981
01:37:15,460 --> 01:37:19,157
I want to thank you
for the support

982
01:37:19,231 --> 01:37:21,166
you've given this campaign.

983
01:37:21,234 --> 01:37:24,431
You made this campaign
the most exciting,

984
01:37:24,504 --> 01:37:28,998
the most important campaign
in this state's history.

985
01:37:29,075 --> 01:37:32,409
I've come here personally
to thank you for that.

986
01:37:42,156 --> 01:37:44,057
Johnny!

987
01:37:48,496 --> 01:37:50,430
Give me him!

988
01:37:50,498 --> 01:37:52,295
Don't!

989
01:37:52,367 --> 01:37:54,528
No!

990
01:37:54,603 --> 01:37:57,471
Sonny! The man's
trying to kill me!

991
01:38:37,072 --> 01:38:39,700
You son of a bitch!

992
01:38:39,774 --> 01:38:42,835
Who sent you?
Huh?

993
01:39:07,138 --> 01:39:09,299
It's over.

994
01:39:13,711 --> 01:39:16,009
You're finished.

995
01:39:18,884 --> 01:39:21,546
Where's that kid
with the camera?

996
01:39:21,620 --> 01:39:23,713
I don't see him.

997
01:39:23,789 --> 01:39:25,484
You asshole!

998
01:39:34,834 --> 01:39:37,803
It's okay.
It's all right.

999
01:39:52,354 --> 01:39:54,720
Oh, Johnny, why?

1000
01:39:55,791 --> 01:39:57,725
Why?

1001
01:40:02,999 --> 01:40:04,990
Good-bye.

1002
01:40:08,704 --> 01:40:10,672
I love you.

